Text: Reminder Credit Risk Modeling for Financial Institutionspst For the first time in nearly two years we will be offering our Executive Education course in Europe Credit Risk Modeling for Financial Institutions Stanford Graduate School of Business Zurich Switzerland March An overview of the course and description of some of the new content of this course can be obtained by contacting us or visiting wwwgsbstanfordeduexedcrm It would be great to see you there Darrell Duffie and Ken Singleton Alicia Steinaecker Isero Program Manager Stanford Executive Program Stanford University Graduate School of Business Memorial Way Stanford California fax
